// BottomTabBar
// Fixed bottom navigation bar for mobile with three tabs: preview, chat,
// terminal. Each tab has an SVG icon and label. Fixed to viewport bottom
// with iOS safe-area padding.

FUNCTION BottomTabBar(activeTab, onTabChange) -> JSX                   EXPORT
  Renders three tab buttons (preview, chat, terminal).
  Active tab is highlighted with accent color; inactive tabs are gray.
  Calls onTabChange with the tab name on click.
